easingly polarizing presence ever since he made a modest $10 million person=
al investment in Musk=E2=80=99s Twitter and where he seems to parrot many o=
f Musk=E2=80=99s obsessions on the platform. Needless to say, few other Wal=
l Street types have taken to X with Ackman=E2=80=99s enthusiasm and alacrit=
y. Many people in my world think that=E2=80=99s a mistake; Bill clearly dis=
agrees.

