e Town</a></u></i>. The only thing I would add to their insights is that if=
 it goes to litigation, which seems more and more likely since the NBA reje=
cted WBD=E2=80=99s matching bid this afternoon, it will be a quasi-holy war=
 between David (quite literally) and Goliath. <br/><br/>As I tried to conve=
y in my <u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z=
